Title:  Small Batch Software

Timestamp: 20210816195427

Seq:    12.6.2

Level:  4 - Subsection

Body: 

There's certainly a place in the world for corporate software built at industrial scale. 

But that's no part of my intention with Notenik. 

My goal is to deliver a modest application that does a few things well, and to continue to deliver small but regular improvements to that software for as long as there's still meaningful work to be done.
